{"type":"message","id":"e1032dbf","parentId":"0bd6dc55","timestamp":"2026-04-19T03:57:22.212Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-19 11:57:19 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b5171672ffca4c380c136d2d9d1c]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5171672ffca4c380c136d2d9d1c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-19 11:57 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\nеҰӮдҪ•жөӢиҜ•иҝҷдёӘskillжҳҜз”ҹж•Ҳзҡ„"}],"timestamp":1776571042198}}
{"type":"message","id":"79182aa5","parentId":"e1032dbf","timestamp":"2026-04-19T03:57:34.305Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how to test if a skill is working/з”ҹж•Ҳ. But they haven't specified which skill they're referring to. Let me check what skills are available and think about what they might mean.\n\nLooking at the available skills listed in the system prompt, there are many skills like:\n- 1688-product-search\n- 1688-ranking\n- alphashop-sel-product-search\n- feishu-bitable\n- feishu-calendar\n- feishu-create-doc\n- feishu-fetch-doc\n- feishu-im-read\n- feishu-task\n- feishu-update-doc\n\n\n- And many more...\n\nSince they haven't specified which skill, I should ask them to clarify. But before doing that, let me consider if there's a more helpful approachвҖ”I could mention the most commonly used skills and how to test them, or ask which specific one they're working with. Given the context, they might be testing one of the Feishu-related skills since those seem most relevant to their setup.\n\nActually, looking back at the message, there's no specific skill mentioned at all. I should just ask them directly which skill they want to test and briefly explain what testing would involve."},{"type":"text","text":"дҪ жҳҜжҢҮе“ӘдёӘ skillпјҹ\n\nдёҖиҲ¬жөӢиҜ• skill з”ҹж•Ҳзҡ„ж–№ејҸжҳҜпјҡ\n\n1. **и°ғз”Ёе®ғзҡ„ж ёеҝғеҠҹиғҪ** вҖ” жҜ”еҰӮжөӢиҜ•йЈһд№Ұ skillпјҢе°ұзңҹзҡ„еҺ»иҜ»еҸ–дёҖдёӘж–ҮжЎЈжҲ–ж—ҘеҺҶ\n2. **еҸ‘йҖҒи§ҰеҸ‘жҢҮд»Ө** вҖ” жҜ”еҰӮеҸ‘йҖҒгҖҢеё®жҲ‘жҗңдёҖдёӢ1688зҡ„XXXгҖҚпјҢзңӢжҳҜеҗҰжңүз»“жһңиҝ”еӣһ\n\nеҰӮжһңдҪ иҝҳжІЎй…ҚзҪ®е…·дҪ“зҡ„ skillпјҢжғізЎ®и®Ө OpenClaw зҡ„ skill зі»з»ҹжҳҜеҗҰжӯЈеёёе·ҘдҪңпјҢеҸҜд»Ҙе‘ҠиҜүжҲ‘дҪ е…іеҝғзҡ„жҳҜе“ӘдёӘ skillпјҲйЈһд№ҰгҖҒ1688гҖҒиҝҳжҳҜеҲ«зҡ„пјүпјҢжҲ‘жқҘеё®дҪ жөӢиҜ•гҖӮ"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason