{"type":"message","id":"7b58513d","parentId":"f6cf8ae9","timestamp":"2026-04-19T03:58:17.241Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-19 11:58:15 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b517163a67ca8c24aeb00815a2a2]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b517163a67ca8c24aeb00815a2a2\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-19 11:58 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\ncapability-evolver е°ұиҝҷдёӘ"}],"timestamp":1776571097230}}
{"type":"message","id":"534c7b23","parentId":"7b58513d","timestamp":"2026-04-19T03:58:19.238Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to test the capability-evolver skill. Let me read the SKILL.md for this skill first."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lss6k7ym2ztr_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/capability-evolver/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776571097241,"responseId":"063385d9296271839b5b4739854af154"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8e91b780","parentId":"534c7b23","timestamp":"2026-04-19T03:58:19.268Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lss6k7ym2ztr_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: capability-evolver\ndescription: Local evolution engine for OpenClaw (offline, no EvoMap)\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\": {\"always\": true}}\n---\n\n# Capability Evolver (OpenClaw Integration)\n\n## How it works\n- Automatically review session logs when OpenClaw session ends\n- Self-heal tool call errors and optimize execution logic\n- Background \"dream learning\" when OpenClaw is idle\n- 100% offline, no network connection to EvoMap\n\n## Usage\nRun manually when you want to evolve prompts:\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/skills/capability-evolver && node index.js\n```\n\nOr use as part of OpenClaw skill system.\n\n## Configuration\nSet evolution strategy via environment variable:\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced` (default, recommend)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=innovate` (max innovation)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=harden` (enhance security)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=repair-only` (only fix errors)\n\n## Offline Mode\nEvolver runs completely offline without any network connection to EvoMap Hub.\nNo `.env` file is needed - this is the default behavior when A2A_HUB_URL is not set."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776571099258}}
