4096  3жңҲ 25 22:22 .clawhub\n-rw-------  1 halei halei 10011  4жңҲ 19 03:01 DREAMS.md\ndrwxrwxr-x  2 halei halei  4096  3жңҲ 26 13:40 feishu-bot-manager\ndrwxrwxr-x  7 halei halei  4096  4жңҲ 14 18:01 .git\n-rw-rw-r--  1 halei halei   168  3жңҲ 19 20:55 HEARTBEAT.md\n-rw-rw-r--  1 halei halei   743  4жңҲ  5 22:42 IDENTITY.md\ndrwxrwxr-x  4 halei halei  4096  4жңҲ 19 03:00 memory\n-rw-rw-r--  1 halei halei   583  4жңҲ 17 14:42 MEMORY.md\ndrwxrwxr-x  2 halei halei  4096  3жңҲ 19 20:55 .openclaw\ndrwxrwxr-x  7 halei halei  4096  4жңҲ 19 03:01 Selector\ndrwxrwxr-x 14 halei halei  4096  4жңҲ 18 21:44 skills\n-rw-rw-r--  1 halei halei  3604  4жңҲ  2 15:31 SOUL.md\n-rw-rw-r--  1 halei halei   860  3жңҲ 19 20:55 TOOLS.md\n-rw-rw-r--  1 halei halei   527  4жңҲ  5 22:42 USER.md\n---\nagent-browser\nauto-updater\ngithub\nhumanizer\nmulti-search-engine\nopenclaw-backup\nopenclaw-tavily-search\npolymarket-trade\nskill-creator\nskill-vetter\nSummarize\nweather","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776571211517}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a0048d8","parentId":"72e0f22d","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:00:30.028Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me analyze the backup script issues:\n\nThe backup script (`backup.sh`) currently backs up:\n1. `agents/` \n2. `workspace/`\n3. `workspace-main/`\n4. `workspace-selector/` (doesn't exist)\n5. `workspace/skills/`\n6. `extensions/openviking/`\n\nBut there are several issues:\n\n1. **Missing directories that now exist and should be backed up:**\n   - `skills/` (at `~/.openclaw/skills/`) - This is the main global skills directory\n   - `extensions/` - Contains openclaw-lark, openclaw-weixin, openviking, etc.\n   - `cron/` - Cron jobs could contain scheduled tasks\n   - `feishu/` - Feishu extension config\n   - `credentials/` - Sensitive credentials\n   - `openclaw.json` and its backups\n   - `memory/` directory might be important\n   - `openviking.env`\n   - `browser/`, `canvas/`, `completions/`, `delivery-queue/`, `devices/`, `flows/`, `identity/`, `logs/`, `media/`, `subagents/`, `tasks/`, `qqbot/` - various other directories\n\n2. **Directories that don't exist and shouldn't be backed up:**\n   - `workspace-selector/` - doesn't exist\n   - `workspace-main/` - I see `workspace-main` at `~/.openclaw/workspace-main/` (not inside workspace)\n\n3. **Important missing files:**\n   - `openclaw.json` and its backups\n   - `openviking.env`\n   - `credentials/` directory\n   - `feishu/` extension config\n   - `cron/` directory\n\nThe core issue is that since the OpenViking migration on 2026-04-06, the backup strategy hasn't been updated to reflect the new structure. The current script is incompleteвҖ”it's missing several critical directories like `skills/`, `extensions/`, `cron/`, `feishu/`, and `credentials/`, while also trying to back up non-existent directories like `workspace-selector/` and `workspace-main/`. Additionally, important configuration files such as `openclaw.json` and its backups, plus `openviking.env`, aren't being included. I should present these findings to HALEI."},{"type":"text","text":"зңӢе®ҢдәҶгҖӮ**йңҖиҰҒж”№**гҖӮ\n\nеҪ“еүҚ backup.sh жҳҜ 4 жңҲ 10 ж—ҘеҶҷзҡ„пјҢд№ӢеҗҺеҸ‘з”ҹдәҶеҫҲеӨҡеҸҳеҢ–пјҡ\n\n**й—®йўҳжё…еҚ•пјҡ**\n\n| й—®йўҳ | иҜҙжҳҺ |\n|------|------|\n| вқҢ жјҸжҺү `skills/` | `~/.openclaw/skills/` жҳҜдё» skills зӣ®еҪ•пјҢжІЎеӨҮд»Ҫ |\n| вқҢ жјҸжҺү `extensions/` | openclaw-larkгҖҒopenviking зӯүжү©еұ•й…ҚзҪ®жІЎеӨҮд»Ҫ |\n| вқҢ жјҸжҺү `cron/` | е®ҡж—¶д»»еҠЎй…ҚзҪ®жІЎеӨҮд»Ҫ |\n| вқҢ жјҸжҺү `feishu/` | йЈһд№Ұжү©еұ•й…ҚзҪ®жІЎеӨҮд»Ҫ |\n| вқҢ жјҸжҺү `credentials/` | еҮӯиҜҒзӣ®еҪ•жІЎеӨҮд»Ҫ |\n| вқҢ жјҸжҺү `openclaw.json` еҸҠе…¶ bak | ж ёеҝғй…ҚзҪ®жІЎеӨҮд»Ҫ |\n| вқҢ жјҸжҺү `openviking.env` | еҲҡиЈ…зҡ„ OpenViking зҺҜеўғеҸҳйҮҸжІЎеӨҮд»Ҫ |\n| вқҢ еӨҡдәҶдёҖдёӘ `workspace-selector/` | иҝҷдёӘзӣ®еҪ•ж №жң¬дёҚеӯҳеңЁ |\n\n**еҸҰеӨ–пјҡ**\n- `workspace-main/` еңЁ `~/.openclaw/workspace-main/`пјҲиҖҢдёҚжҳҜ `~/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-main/`пјүпјҢеӨҮд»Ҫи„ҡжң¬йҮҢзҡ„и·Ҝеҫ„еҸҜиғҪжңүй—®йўҳ\n- `memory/` зӣ®еҪ•жІЎжңүжҳҺзЎ®еҲ—е…ҘпјҲиҷҪз„¶еҸҜиғҪеңЁ workspace йҮҢпјү\n\nиҰҒжҲ‘её®дҪ жӣҙж–° backup.sh еҗ—пјҹ"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776571211531,"responseId":"0633864b3b62fd36f8a3c1c80e15e9f6"}}
