{"type":"message","id":"e627ea03","parentId":"663ae165","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:05:01.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a full picture. Let me also check what's currently in the repo's root level vs what exists locally.\n\nLocal `.openclaw/`:\n- `agents/` вң… in backup\n- `credentials/` вқҢ NOT in backup\n- `cron/` вң… in backup\n- `devices/` вң… in backup\n- `extensions/` - openclaw-lark, openviking, openclawwechat, openclaw-weixin вқҢ NOT in backup (only openviking was backed up from extensions/ subdir)\n- `feishu/` вқҢ NOT in backup\n- `flows/` вң… in backup\n- `identity/` вң… in backup\n\n\n- `memory/` вқҢ NOT in backup\n- `skills/` вң… in backup (capability-evolver and vibesurf are both there)\n- `subagents/` вқҢ NOT in backup\n- `workspace/` вң… in backup\n- `workspace-main/` вң… in backup\n- `workspace-selector/` вң… in backup but doesn't exist locally\n\nI'm also noticing some directories that shouldn't be tracked like canvas, completions, logs, and delivery-queue are actually included in the backup.\n\nLooking at the root level backup structure, I see media, tasks, and .github are backed up. I should also check if openviking.env and openclaw.json need to be included. The key gaps for the user are that openclaw.json has multiple backup versions but the main file isn't being tracked, and openviking.env which is specific to the openviking extension is missing. The extensions directory with openclaw-lark and openclaw-weixin isn't being backed up, nor is feishu/ or the memory directory, while the workspace skills folder with all the user-installed skills is only partially covered.\n\nThe old backup script was using rsync to sync agents, workspace, workspace-main, workspace-selector, and workspace skills, but it stopped short of including the extensions directory which is where the actual openclaw extensions like openviking live. I need to write a proper backup structure that captures all these missing pieces."},{"type":"text","text":"жғ…еҶөе…ЁйғЁж‘ёжё…дәҶгҖӮжқҘж•ҙзҗҶпјҡ\n\n---\n\n## еӨҮд»Ҫз»“жһ„е…ЁиІҢ\n\n**GitHub д»“еә“е·ІжңүпјҲжҢүж—Ҙжңҹеӯҳж”ҫпјүпјҡ**\n`agents/` `cron/` `delivery-queue/` `devices/` `flows/` `identity/` `skills/` `workspace/` `workspace-main/` `workspace-selector/`\n\n**жң¬ең° `.openclaw/` е®һйҷ…зӣ®еҪ•пјҡ**\n```\n.openclaw/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ agents/                    вҶҗ вң… е·ІеңЁ backup\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ credentials/               вҶҗ вқҢ зјәеӨұпјҲеҜҶй’Ҙзұ»пјү\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ cron/                      вҶҗ вң… е·ІеңЁ backup\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ devices/                   вҶҗ вң… е·ІеңЁ backup\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ extensions/                вҶҗ вқҢ зјәеӨұпјҲеӨ§йҮҸй…ҚзҪ®пјү\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw-lark/         вҶҗ йЈһд№Ұжү©еұ•\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw-weixin/       вҶҗ еҫ®дҝЎжү©еұ•\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ openclawwechat/        вҶҗ еҫ®дҝЎжү©еұ•\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ openviking/            вҶҗ вқҢ еҸӘжңүйғЁеҲҶпјҢextensions/openviking/ жІЎеңЁ backup.sh йҮҢ\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ feishu/                    вҶҗ вқҢ зјәеӨұ\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ flows/                     вҶҗ вң… е·ІеңЁ backup\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ identity/                  вҶҗ вң… е·ІеңЁ backup\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ memory/                    вҶҗ вқҢ зјәеӨұпјҲ.dreams еңЁиҝҷпјү\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ skills/                    вҶҗ вқҢ зјәеӨұпјҲcapability-evolverгҖҒvibesurf еңЁиҝҷпјү\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ capability-evolver/    вҶҗ evolver еҹәеӣ еә“\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ vibesurf/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ subagents/                 вҶҗ вқҢ зјәеӨұ\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ workspace/                 вҶҗ вң… е·ІеңЁ backup\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ workspace-main/            вҶҗ вң… е·ІеңЁ backup\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw.json              вҶҗ вқҢ зјәеӨұ\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw.json.bak*         вҶҗ вқҢ зјәеӨұ\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ openviking.env             вҶҗ вқҢ зјәеӨұ\nв””в”Җв”Җ memory/                   вҶҗ вқҢ зјәеӨұ\n    в””в”Җв”Җ .dreams/               вҶҗ evolver иҜӯж–ҷ/и®°еҝҶж•°жҚ®\n```\n\n**capability-evolver зӣёе…іж•°жҚ®пјҲиҰҒдёҚиҰҒеӨҮд»Ҫпјүпјҡ**\n\n| ж•°жҚ® | и·Ҝеҫ„ | е»әи®® |\n|------|------|------|\n| Dream дјҡиҜқиҜӯж–ҷ | `~/.openclaw/workspace/memory