{"type":"message","id":"bf8c438e","parentId":"4994c56a","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:09:08.994Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-19 12:09:04 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b51711b3304a8c2e5153261edd3c]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51711b3304a8c2e5153261edd3c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-19 12:09 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\nopenclaw.json иҝҷдёӘж–ҮжЎЈйғҪзјәеӨұ пјҢйӮЈиҝҳеӨҮд»Ҫд»Җд№ҲпјҢ"}],"timestamp":1776571748974}}
{"type":"message","id":"a763c4fc","parentId":"bf8c438e","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:09:31.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is frustrated that openclaw.json wasn't being backed up and thinks the backup is incomplete. Let me write a new comprehensive backup.sh that includes all the necessary paths. Let me figure out what the actual state is first - the GitHub repo already has some directories. Let me just write a proper backup.sh now."},{"type":"text","text":"зЎ®е®һиҜҙеҫ—еҜ№гҖӮ`openclaw.json` жҳҜж ёеҝғй…ҚзҪ®пјҢжІЎжңүе®ғе…¶д»–еӨҮд»ҪйғҪжІЎж„Ҹд№үгҖӮзҺ°еңЁе°ұеҶҷпјҡ\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k6efesy3cfcd_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/backup.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Daily Backup Script (updated 2026-04-19)\n# Backs up to GitHub: github.com/59330857/openclaw-backup\n\nBACKUP_REPO=\"/tmp/openclaw-backup-clone\"\nOPENCLAW_DIR=\"$HOME/.openclaw\"\nGIT_REF=\"main\"\nDATE_DIR=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\n\n# Get GH token from gh config\nGH_TOKEN=$(grep \"oauth_token:\" ~/.config/gh/hosts.yml | awk '{print $2}')\n\nset -e\n\necho \"[$(date)] Starting OpenClaw backup...\"\n\n# Clone or update backup repo\nif [ -d \"$BACKUP_REPO/.git\" ]; then\n  cd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\n  git checkout \"$GIT_REF\" 2>/dev/null\n  git pull origin \"$GIT_REF\" --quiet\nelse\n  rm -rf \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\n  git clone \"https://${GH_TOKEN}@github.com/59330857/openclaw-backup.git\" \"$BACKUP_REPO\" --quiet\nfi\n\n# Today's incremental backup (daily snapshots)\nmkdir -p \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR\"\n\n# 1. Core config\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw.json\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw.json.bak\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw.json.bak.1\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openviking.env\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 2. Config directories\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/agents/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/agents/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/credentials/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/credentials/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/cron/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/cron/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/devices/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/devices/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/flows/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/flows/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/identity/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/identity/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/feishu/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/feishu/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/subagents/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/subagents/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 3. Extensions (full directory, not just openviking)\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/extensions/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/extensions/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 4. Skills (main skills directory)\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/skills/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/skills/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 5. Workspace (main + main-workspace)\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/workspace/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-main/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/workspace-main/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 6. Memory & dreams (capability-evolver data)\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/memory/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/memory/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$HOME/.evomap/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/evomap/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 7. QQ bot & WeChat\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/qqbot/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/qqbot/\" 2>/dev/null || true\nrsync -a --delete \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw-weixin/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/openclaw-weixin/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# Commit and push\ncd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\nif git diff --quiet && git diff --cached --quiet && [ ! -d \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/agents\" ] && [ ! -d \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/workspace\" ]; then\n  echo \"[$(date)] No changes, skipping commit\"\nelse\n  git config user.email \"backup@openclaw\"\n  git config user.name \"OpenClaw Backup\"\n  git add -A\n  git commit -m \"Full backup $DATE_DIR $(date '+%H:%M')\"\n  git push origin \"$GIT_REF\"\n  echo \"[$(date)] Backup pushed to GitHub\"\nfi\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776571748994,"responseId":"0633886541d9d6614446f0191f3e9a0b"}}
