{"type":"message","id":"d23def18","parentId":"f917f301","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:10:13.583Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking to confirm the backup strategy - whether we're backing up the entire `~/.openclaw/` directory to GitHub every day.\n\nLet me clarify what the new backup.sh actually does vs what they might be thinking:\n\n1. It backs up specific subdirectories and files, not everything (e.g., it excludes logs/, media/, canvas/, .cache/, delivery-queue/, browser/, tasks/, completions/)\n2. It stores each day's backup in a dated directory (e.g., `2026-04-19/`)\n\nSo yes, it's daily incremental snapshots stored by date in the GitHub repo. But it's not a full mirror of everything in `.openclaw/` - we exclude large/unnecessary stuff."},{"type":"text","text":"жҳҜзҡ„пјҢдҪҶжңүйҖүжӢ©ең°еӨҮд»ҪвҖ”вҖ”дёҚжҳҜе…ЁйҮҸпјҡ\n\n**еӨҮд»Ҫзҡ„еҶ…е®№пјҡ** й…ҚзҪ®ж–Үд»¶гҖҒд»Јз ҒгҖҒи®°еҝҶж•°жҚ®гҖҒе·ҘдҪңеҢә\n\n**жҳҺзЎ®жҺ’йҷӨзҡ„пјҡ**\n- `logs/` `media/` `canvas/` `completions/` вҖ” ж—Ҙеҝ—е’Ңдёҙж—¶ж–Үд»¶\n- `browser/` `tasks/` `delivery-queue/` `node_modules/` вҖ” иҝҗиЎҢж—¶дә§з”ҹзҡ„\n- `.cache/` вҖ” ж— йңҖеӨҮд»Ҫ\n\n**GitHub д»“еә“йҮҢзҡ„з»“жһ„пјҡ**\n```\nopenclaw-backup/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ 2026-04-19/      вҶҗ д»ҠеӨ©\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw.json\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ agents/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ workspace/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ memory/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ skills/\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ ...\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ 2026-04-18/      вҶҗ жҳЁеӨ©\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ ...\nв””в”Җв”Җ 2026-04-10/      вҶҗ жӣҙж—©зҡ„\n```\n\nжҜҸеӨ©еўһйҮҸеӯҳдёҖдёӘж—Ҙжңҹзӣ®еҪ•пјҢдёҚиҰҶзӣ–ж—§ж—ҘжңҹгҖӮиҝҷж ·е“ӘеӨ©еҮәй—®йўҳеҸҜд»Ҙеӣһж»ҡеҲ°д»»ж„ҸдёҖеӨ©гҖӮ"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776571802610,"responseId":"0633889ac00982f3b9dfabdeeeb14c4d"}}
