{"type":"message","id":"e3e9bc2d","parentId":"9acf9b57","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:22:35.267Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script is getting SIGKILLed again. This is the same issue. Let me check if the issue is `set -e` causing the script to exit early. \n\nWait, actually the issue might be that `rsync_safe` is using `|| true` so it shouldn't fail... but `set -e` might be causing issues with some other command.\n\nLet me rewrite the script to be simpler and more robust, without `set -e` and with explicit error handling."},{"type":"text","text":"и„ҡжң¬иў« SIGKILLпјҢеҸҜиғҪжҳҜ `set -e` еңЁжҹҗдәӣиҫ№з•Ңжғ…еҶөдёӢжҠҠж•ҙдёӘи„ҡжң¬жқҖдәҶгҖӮж”№жҲҗжӣҙеҒҘеЈ®зҡ„зүҲжң¬пјҡ\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mdnebbieyz0x_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/backup.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Daily Backup Script (updated 2026-04-19)\n\nBACKUP_REPO=\"/tmp/openclaw-backup-clone\"\nOPENCLAW_DIR=\"$HOME/.openclaw\"\nGIT_REF=\"main\"\nDATE_DIR=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\n\nGH_TOKEN=$(grep \"oauth_token:\" ~/.config/gh/hosts.yml | awk '{print $2}')\n\necho \"[$(date)] Starting OpenClaw backup...\"\n\n# Clone or update backup repo\nif [ -d \"$BACKUP_REPO/.git\" ]; then\n  cd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\n  git checkout \"$GIT_REF\" 2>/dev/null\n  git pull origin \"$GIT_REF\" --quiet\nelse\n  rm -rf \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\n  git clone \"https://${GH_TOKEN}@github.com/59330857/openclaw-backup.git\" \"$BACKUP_REPO\" --quiet\nfi\n\nmkdir -p \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR\"\n\n# rsync with .git excluded\ndo_rsync() {\n  local src=\"$1\"\n  local dst=\"$2\"\n  if [ -e \"$src\" ]; then\n    rsync -a --exclude='.git' --delete \"$src\" \"$dst\"\n  fi\n}\n\n# 1. Core config files\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw.json\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw.json.bak\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw.json.bak.1\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openviking.env\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\n\n# 2. Config directories\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/agents/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/credentials/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/cron/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/devices/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/flows/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/identity/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/feishu/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/subagents/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\n\n# 3. Extensions\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/extensions/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\n\n# 4. Skills\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/skills/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\n\n# 5. Workspace\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-main/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\n\n# 6. Memory & dreams (capability-evolver data)\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/memory/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$HOME/.evomap/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/evomap/\"\n\n# 7. QQ bot & WeChat\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/qqbot/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw-weixin/\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/\"\n\n# Commit and push\ncd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\nHAS_CHANGES=0\nif [ -n \"$(git status --porcelain)\" ]; then\n  HAS_CHANGES=1\nfi\n\nif [ \"$HAS_CHANGES\" = \"1\" ]; then\n  git config user.email \"backup@openclaw\"\n  git config user.name \"OpenClaw Backup\"\n  git add -A\n  git commit -m \"Full backup $DATE_DIR $(date '+%H:%M')\"\n  git push origin \"$GIT_REF\"\n  echo \"[$(date)] Backup pushed to GitHub\"\nelse\n  echo \"[$(date)] No changes, skipping commit\"\nfi\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776572538