{"type":"message","id":"bd9994e7","parentId":"8473fde7","timestamp":"2026-04-19T05:10:01.759Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HALEI is explaining that many people compare Hermes with OpenClaw, saying Hermes can self-evolve. But actually Hermes's core self-evolution feature is copied from the EvoMap/evolver project. HALEI installed capability-evolver for me (OpenClaw) because of this comparison - to make sure I also have the genuine self-evolution capability.\n\nThis is a backhanded compliment - HALEI is saying that Hermes markets itself as having self-iteration capabilities that are actually just copied from the open-source evolver project, while OpenClaw (me) has the legitimate installed version.\n\n\nSince the whole point of capability-evolver is that it analyzes session logs and evolves based on signals from actual usage, it should be getting smarter every time it runs. I should check the current cycle status to see if it's actually making progress."},{"type":"text","text":"еҺҹжқҘеҰӮжӯӨгҖӮиЈ… capability-evolver жҳҜдёәдәҶеҜ№ж Ү Hermes зҡ„\"иҮӘжҲ‘иҝӯд»Ј\"ж ҮзӯҫпјҢиҖҢдё”иЈ…зҡ„жҳҜжӯЈзүҲжәҗеӨҙгҖӮ\n\nиҜҙе®һиҜқиҝҷдёӘзӯ–з•ҘжҢәеҘҪзҡ„вҖ”вҖ”и®©еҜ№жҜ”зҡ„дәәзңӢеҲ°пјҢдёӨиҫ№йғҪжңүиҝҷдёӘиғҪеҠӣпјҢдҪҶ OpenClaw иҝҷдёӘжҳҜеҺҹзүҲгҖӮ\n\nдёҚиҝҮ capability-evolver д»ҠеӨ©и·‘зҡ„йӮЈиҪ®ж•ҲжһңдҪ д№ҹзңӢеҲ°дәҶпјҢе®ғдё»иҰҒиҝҳжҳҜеңЁж•ҙзҗҶи®°еҝҶе’ҢеҶҷ dream diaryпјҢзңҹжӯЈзҡ„д»Јз Ғзә§иҮӘжҲ‘дҝ®еӨҚиҝҳжІЎи§ҰеҸ‘гҖӮзӯүе®ғеӨҡи·‘еҮ еӨ©гҖҒз§ҜзҙҜжӣҙеӨҡ signalпјҢж•ҲжһңдјҡжӣҙжҳҺжҳҫгҖӮ"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776575391076,"responseId":"0633969f869d949f289d753d2e5d947e"}}
