{"type":"message","id":"71a3772b","parentId":"38af75bc","timestamp":"2026-04-19T05:12:54.512Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying:\n1. They don't write code currently\n2. They need to finalize the product selection (йҖүе“Ғ) workflow today with me\n3. They want the product selection agent to run through all the processes\n4. Web Surf project uses too many system resources\n5. The current computer running OpenClaw only has 4GB RAM, so before getting a Mac mini, Web Surf is too resource-heavy\n6. They're switching to using CDP (Chrome DevTools Protocol) via OpenClaw's built-in browser control to handle GUI Chrome\n\nSo they're describing the context for why they're using CDP instead of Web Surf. \n\nNow I need to align on the product selection workflow they want to establish. They mentioned the current setup has 4GB RAM and they're planning to get a Mac mini, but right now they need to work with what's available. I should ask them to walk me through the specific product selection process they want to automate so I can help them set that up properly."},{"type":"text","text":"жҳҺзҷҪпјҢ4G еҶ…еӯҳи·‘ Web Surf зЎ®е®һеҗғеҠӣгҖӮCDP жҺ§еҲ¶жң¬ең° Chrome жҳҜжӣҙиҪ»йҮҸзҡ„ж–№жЎҲпјҢеҶ…еӯҳеҚ з”Ёдјҡе°ҸеҫҲеӨҡгҖӮ\n\nйҖүе“ҒжөҒзЁӢвҖ”вҖ”жқҘеҜ№дёҖдёӢпјҢдҪ еёҢжңӣеҗ„дёӘ Agent иҙҹиҙЈе“ӘдәӣзҺҜиҠӮпјҹ\n\nжҜ”еҰӮеёёи§Ғзҡ„й“ҫи·ҜжҳҜпјҡ\n\n**1688 жүҫиҙ§ вҶ’ зӯӣйҖүж•°жҚ® вҶ’ еҸ‘еёғеҲ°е№іеҸ° вҶ’ иҝҪиёӘз»“жһң**\n\nзӣ®еүҚе“ӘдәӣзҺҜиҠӮе·Із»ҸйҖҡдәҶпјҢе“ӘдәӣиҝҳеҚЎзқҖпјҹ"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776575563197,"responseId":"0633974b94eaa2fa40e3ce913f474294"}}
