{"type":"message","id":"cde0ca24","parentId":"3dd25821","timestamp":"2026-04-19T08:38:30.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The screenshot shows a Hermes management UI that's trying to connect to localhost:9119 (web) and localhost:8642 (API). But the Hermes container exposes port 18788 for the gateway.\n\nLet me check what ports the current hermes-agent container actually has exposed and what services are running inside it."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_72etzf2xtuxg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker exec hermes-agent /opt/hermes/.venv/bin/hermes status 2>&1 | grep -E \"port|Port|API|api|web|Web|URL|url\" | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776587904838,"responseId":"0633c7814c0a67e757c580f5c99972a8"}}
